dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Shawano County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Shawano_Zoning_2016.gdb'. The features included in this geodatabase are 'FARMLAND' and 'GENERAL'. [Zoning coverage showing the areas that fall under the jurisdiction of the Shawano county zoning ordinance.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
